{"tid":726730,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"改歌：婚紗背後","createTime":"2018-07-02T15:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T15:34:42.000Z","uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"26a9d4cb10698fc7fa74c2f1bc08008eb97b82fa","tid":726730,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"仍然說笑　即使這是苦笑<br />\n望著嘉賓　將他慶賀呼叫<br />\n奏著仍係昨天的曲調<br />\n或者今天彈得更妙<br />\n<br />\n仍然祝福　祝福這段婚宴<br />\n望著婚紗　婚紗背後的臉<br />\n你是誰　共你未見一面<br />\n卻已經令我心酸<br />\n<br />\n未想講多半句　唯恐怕會落淚<br />\n緣已盡不可追　理由誰可領會<br />\n讓孤單加空虛　讓當初都過去<br />\n縱有癡心　仍難定散聚<br />\n<br />\n婚紗中背影一起遠去<br />\n走去蜜月甜夢裡<br />\n我但願前事跟他遠去<br />\n讓我的心　安靜如水"},{"pid":"c3feb3d40df471a814c365ad3148fb9b9fcb296c","tid":726730,"uid":6783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T16:20:27.000Z","msg":"改左d咩"},{"pid":"9176789f193ace52daa3d87d4ff6bed682b4091a","tid":726730,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T16:49:08.000Z","msg":"仍然說笑　儘管這是家燕<br />\n望著粒癦　給她慶賀呼叫"},{"pid":"7ca87b86334ae63847829a391f61f8687b917228","tid":726730,"uid":169155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T18:48:07.000Z","msg":"呢首歌淨係100毛都改編過兩次"},{"pid":"0bc4ab6d139a250c18fcec1076a2d2fa4d42191c","tid":726730,"uid":161115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T18:49:28.000Z","msg":"樓豬妙改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2b665c3ac1a0e8156db0b60b59494f2656edd7","tid":726730,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9176789f193ace52daa3d87d4ff6bed682b4091a","tid":726730,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T16:49:08.000Z","msg":"仍然說笑　儘管這是家燕<br />\n望著粒癦　給她慶賀呼叫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=